{"title":"讲词","authors":["罗勃特·海顿"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔美国〕　罗勃特·海顿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我说，白人兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑人兄弟，听我说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑人的痛苦身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给电火烧成一团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只开电门的手，我见过；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白人的罢工队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然遭到了射击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只打暗号的手，我见过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们是同一只手呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟们，听我说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们是同一只手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我说，黑人兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白人兄弟，听我说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听过他们说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一句都像一道铁丝网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬要把你们隔开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听他们这样说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“臭黑奴！”“穷白鬼！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话的是同一个人呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟们，千万听清楚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话的是同一个人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔王佐良译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}